    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200\u00b0C/ 180\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Put a large baking tray (or two) in the oven to heat up (this will stop the pizza bottoms from going soggy!)</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-nduja-and-pepperoni-pizza/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> to a bowl with the<strong> chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Add 5 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[7 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[10 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong> and give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>tomato base</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-nduja-and-pepperoni-pizza/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Drain and pat your <strong>mozzarella</strong> dry with kitchen paper (squeeze as much liquid out as you can!)</p><p>Tear the drained mozzarella into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-nduja-and-pepperoni-pizza/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray[s] from the oven and add your <strong>pizza base[s]</strong></p><p>Spread the <strong>tomato base</strong> evenly over your pizza base[s] with the back of a spoon</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-nduja-and-pepperoni-pizza/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Top the pizza[s] with your <strong>sliced pepperoni</strong> and <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>'Nduja</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>torn mozzarella</strong> and your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 15-17 min or until the cheese has melted and the bases are crisp \u2013 this is your <strong>spicy 'Nduja & pepperoni pizza</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-nduja-and-pepperoni-pizza/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the pizza is in the oven, combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and<strong> black pepper</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>balsamic dressing</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-nduja-and-pepperoni-pizza/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper<strong> </strong>and drizzle over the <strong>balsamic dressing</strong></p><p>Mix it all together \u2013 this is your<strong> balsamic salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-nduja-and-pepperoni-pizza/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy 'Nduja & pepperoni pizza </strong>with the <strong>balsamic salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
